  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK320">
<l>nōyellā nōyceytār mēlavā nōyceyyār</l>
<l>nōyiṉmai vēṇṭu pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sorrow will come upon those who cause pain to others; therefore those, who desire to be free from sorrow, give no pain to others.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
